damaged_parts.name: Front bumper cover
damaged_parts.description: The front bumper cover has sustained moderate deformation, likely due to a collision. The damage is visible across a significant portion of the bumper.
damaged_parts.notes: Repair involves reshaping and refinishing the bumper cover to restore its original form.

damaged_parts.name: Front grille
damaged_parts.description: The front grille shows moderate deformation, affecting its alignment and appearance. This may impact airflow to the radiator.
damaged_parts.notes: Realignment and minor repairs are necessary to restore functionality and aesthetics.

damaged_parts.name: Front left fender
damaged_parts.description: The front left fender has moderate deformation, likely from an impact. The damage affects the fender's shape and may interfere with the wheel well.
damaged_parts.notes: Repair will involve reshaping and possibly refinishing the fender.

damaged_parts.name: Front left headlight
damaged_parts.description: The front left headlight is cracked, compromising its structural integrity and potentially affecting light output.
damaged_parts.notes: Replacement is recommended to ensure proper visibility and safety.

damaged_parts.name: Front right fender
damaged_parts.description: The front right fender exhibits moderate deformation, which may affect the vehicle's aerodynamics and appearance.
damaged_parts.notes: Reshaping and refinishing will be required to restore the fender.

damaged_parts.name: Front right headlight
damaged_parts.description: The front right headlight is cracked, which may lead to moisture ingress and reduced lighting performance.
damaged_parts.notes: Replacement is necessary to maintain optimal lighting conditions.

damaged_parts.name: Front bumper cover
damaged_parts.description: The front bumper cover is missing, exposing underlying components and affecting the vehicle's safety and aesthetics.
damaged_parts.notes: A new bumper cover must be installed to restore the vehicle's appearance and protection.

damaged_parts.name: Front left fender
damaged_parts.description: The front left fender has moderate deformation, affecting its alignment and potentially the door gap.
damaged_parts.notes: Repair will involve reshaping and refinishing to ensure proper fit and finish.

summary.comments: The vehicle has sustained significant damage to the front end, affecting both structural and lighting components. Repairs will require a combination of part replacements and refinishing, with safety systems potentially impacted by the missing bumper cover.
